                        <interp inst="t18521213-113-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 25.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">DEVONPORT</hi>—
<rs id="t18521213-113-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18521213-113-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
