                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">on</hi> 2<hi rend="italic">nd</hi> 
                     <hi rend="smallCaps">COUNT</hi>
                  </rs>. Aged 23.—(<hi rend="italic">See Third Court, Wednesday.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Wright was further charged with having been before convicted.</hi>
               </p>
